{"tid":691533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(無恥黑警）警官涉毒而停職  11年間竟照逗58萬港元人工！！！！！","createTime":"2018-06-05T23:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T04:21:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e92e5fe5b2246efeb64841715e210c34cbb5d31f","tid":691533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T23:42:09.000Z","msg":"加拿大多倫多一名涉毒警官，但被停職的11年間甚麼也不用做，仍可照拿取9.6萬加元（約58萬港元）年薪。警官至周一（5日）終於被解僱，但他隨即上訴，聲稱要「捍衞自己的工作」，獲准繼續支薪，暫時毋須執行有關懲罰。 <br />\n<br />\n在2007年，多倫多警方調查一個跨國販毒集團，將大麻和可卡因走私到美加的案件時，發現現年36歲的弗洛里亞（Loan-Florin Floria）涉案其中。他涉嫌利用職務之便，協助及包庇在販毒集團中的友人。弗洛里亞被控洗錢、協助綁架以及妨礙司法公正等罪名，一直被停職；至2012年，他獲判無罪。 <br />\n<br />\n弗洛里亞的刑事控罪獲撤銷，惟他仍面對警察內部紀律聆訊11項指控。其中在2005年，一名認識弗洛里亞的受害人，向前者表示遭人毆打和折磨，及要求交贖金後，弗洛里亞要求受害人不要報警，稱會調查事件。控方指，弗洛里亞私下調查，純粹是想保護兩名毒販朋友。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，弗洛里亞又一登入警察內部資料庫，將機密信息外洩。退休警司普勒斯頓（Debra Preston）在聽證會後，指弗洛里亞涉及嚴重不當行為，性格上有缺陷的他，不是懲教可改變，解僱成唯一選擇。弗洛里亞認為判決不公，隨即向委員會提出上訴，獲准繼續停職留薪。"},{"pid":"e05bc99cd9190872a773d23f4431d0bf3306c8db","tid":691533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff83568477d19f764fab9a9366aa274fa4cc248","tid":691533,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"黑警無國界<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d656a7f535a167f06f09f2a0b3b2c5e8e002b7","tid":691533,"uid":164913,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:51:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7086570e05106ee22a647934064e8c59d3ca6086","tid":691533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aac056b7bd2066a6ef7d06c1b18b59589e10cd8","tid":691533,"uid":86893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"You did nothing wrong<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da0ae9f22e8eebde884e799e1bfffa412750c52","tid":691533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7591bbfa338c884fa801e7d2a441f29c830bc34","tid":691533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5544710310b9c4cbeb1930abfd1ac5cf9b4932da","tid":691533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3f0bfdba417daae68b7c03a0ef25a0e42b1a55","tid":691533,"uid":20072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/122150_da36a5b9f82e696ad110bda019b1dc6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F122150_da36a5b9f82e696ad110bda019b1dc6d.png&h=badea30d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}